<!-- Linking data to operational needs --><div style="margin-top:12px;border:1px solid #e8eef6;border-radius:16px;background:#ffffff;padding:16px 18px;">
<div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:900;color:#0e1e3d;margin-bottom:10px;">Linking asset data to operational needs</div>
<div style="color:#5b6b88;line-height:1.65;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;">Once maintainable assets are identified, the next step is to understand why information about these assets is required. Each data requirement should support a clear operational decision or action.</div>
