<!-- Why this matters callout --><div style="margin-top:12px;background:#fbfdff;border:1px solid #dbe6f3;border-left:5px solid #009ef5;border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px;color:#0e1e3d;">
<div style="font-weight:950;color:#1c2430;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:6px;">Why this matters</div>
<div style="color:#5b6b88;line-height:1.65;font-size:14px;">Identifying maintainable assets ensures that information requirements remain operationally focused. By defining which assets matter and why, asset data can be structured consistently later without overloading the project with unnecessary information.</div>
</div>
